#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:81
msgid ""
"Localization settings are based on three components: the language code, country code, and encoding.  Locale names are "
"constructed from these parts as follows:"
msgstr "本地化设置主要基于三个部分：语言代码、国家代码和编码。本地化名称是由这些部分构成的，如下所示："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:85
#, no-wrap
