"The _LanguageCode_ and _CountryCode_ are used to determine the country and the specific language variation.  <<locale-lang-"
"country>> provides some examples of __LanguageCode_CountryCode__:"
msgstr ""
"语言代码（LanguageCode）和国家代码（CountryCode）用于确定国家和具体的语言变化。通用语言和国家代码提供了一些语言代码国家代码的例"
"子。"

