msgstr "% locale\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:123
msgid ""
"Language specific character sets, such as ISO8859-1, ISO8859-15, KOI8-R, and CP437, are described in man:multibyte[3].  The "
"active list of character sets can be found at the http://www.iana.org/assignments/character-sets[IANA Registry]."
msgstr ""
"特定语言的字符集，如 ISO8859-1、ISO8859-15、KOI8-R 和 CP437，在 man:multibyte[3] 中描述。有效的字符集列表可以在 "
"http://www.iana.org/assignments/character-sets[IANA Registry] 找到。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:128
msgid ""
"Some languages, such as Chinese or Japanese, cannot be represented using ASCII characters and require an extended language "
"encoding using either wide or multibyte characters.  Examples of wide or multibyte encodings include EUC and Big5.  Older "
"applications may mistake these encodings for control characters while newer applications usually recognize these characters.  "
"Depending on the implementation, users may be required to compile an application with wide or multibyte character support, or "
"to configure it correctly."
msgstr ""
"有些语言，如中文或日文，不能用 ASCII 字符表示，需要用宽字符或多字节字符进行扩展语言编码。宽字符或多字节编码的例子包括 EUC 和 "
"Big5。旧的应用程序可能会误认为这些编码是控制字符，而新的应用程序通常会识别这些字符。根据不同的实现，用户可能需要编译一个支持宽字"
"符或多字节字符的应用程序，或者对其进行正确的配置。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:132
msgid "FreeBSD uses Xorg-compatible locale encodings."
msgstr "FreeBSD 使用与 Xorg 兼容的地区编码。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:136
msgid ""
"The rest of this section describes the various methods for configuring the locale on a FreeBSD system.  The next section will "
"discuss the considerations for finding and compiling applications with i18n support."
msgstr "本节的其余部分将描述在 FreeBSD 系统上配置 locale 的各种方法。下一节将讨论寻找和编译支持 i18n 的应用程序的注意事项。"

#. type: Title ===
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:138
#, no-wrap
msgid "Setting Locale for Login Shell"
msgstr "为登录 shell 设置地区设置"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:141
msgid ""
"Locale settings are configured either in a user's [.filename]#~/.login_conf# or in the startup file of the user's shell: [."
"filename]#~/.profile#, [.filename]#~/.bashrc#, or [.filename]#~/.cshrc#."
msgstr "" 
"地区设置是在用户的 [.filename]#~/.login_conf# 或用户 shell 的启动文件中配置的：[.filename]#~/.profile#、 [.filename]#~/.bashrc# "
"或 [.filename]#~/.cshrc#。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:143
msgid "Two environment variables should be set:"
msgstr "有两个环境变量应该被设置："

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:145
msgid "`LANG`, which sets the locale"
msgstr "`LANG`，用于设置语言环境。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:146
msgid "`MM_CHARSET`, which sets the MIME character set used by applications"
msgstr "`MM_CHARSET`,设置应用程序使用的MIME字符集。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:148
msgid ""
"In addition to the user's shell configuration, these variables should also be set for specific application configuration and "
"Xorg configuration."
msgstr "除了用户的 shell 配置之外，这些变量还应该为特定的应用程序配置和 Xorg 配置而设置。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:151
msgid ""
"Two methods are available for making the needed variable assignments: the <<login-class,login class>> method, which is the "
"recommended method, and the <<startup-file,startup file>> method.  The next two sections demonstrate how to use both methods."
msgstr "有两种方法可用于进行所需的变量分配：登录类方法，这是推荐的方法，以及启动文件方法。接下来的两节将演示如何使用这两种方法。"

#. type: Title ====
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:153
#, no-wrap
msgid "Login Classes Method"
msgstr "登录类方法"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:157
msgid ""
"This first method is the recommended method as it assigns the required environment variables for locale name and MIME character "
"sets for every possible shell.  This setup can either be performed by each user or it can be configured for all users by the "
"superuser."
msgstr ""
"这第一种方法是推荐的方法，因为它为每个可能的 shell 分配了所需的环境变量，如 locale name 和 MIME 字符集。这个设置可以由每个用户执"
"行，也可以由超级用户为所有用户配置。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:159
msgid ""
"This minimal example sets both variables for Latin-1 encoding in the [.filename]#.login_conf# of an individual user's home "
"directory:"
msgstr "这个最小的例子在单个用户的主目录的 [.filename]#.login_conf# 中为 Latin-1 编码设置了两个变量："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:165
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"me:\\\n"
"\t:charset=ISO-8859-1:\\\n"
"\t:lang=de_DE.ISO8859-1:\n"
msgstr ""
"me:\\\n"
"\t:charset=ISO-8859-1:\\\n"
"\t:lang=de_DE.ISO8859-1:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:169
msgid ""
"Here is an example of a user's [.filename]#~/.login_conf# that sets the variables for Traditional Chinese in BIG-5 encoding.  "
"More variables are needed because some applications do not correctly respect locale variables for Chinese, Japanese, and Korean:"
msgstr ""
"下面是一个用户的 [.filename]#~/.login_conf# 的例子，它为 BIG-5 编码的繁体中文设置了变量。因为有些应用程序不能正确地尊重中文、日"
"文和韩文的地域变量，所以需要设置更多的变量："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:179
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"#Users who do not wish to use monetary units or time formats\n"
"#of Taiwan can manually change each variable\n"
"me:\\\n"
"\t:lang=zh_TW.Big5:\\\n"
"\t:setenv=LC_ALL=zh_TW.Big5,LC_COLLATE=zh_TW.Big5,LC_CTYPE=zh_TW.Big5,LC_MESSAGES=zh_TW.Big5,LC_MONETARY=zh_TW.Big5,LC_NUMERIC=zh_TW.Big5,LC_TIME=zh_TW.Big5:\\\n"
"\t:charset=big5:\\\n"
"\t:xmodifiers=\"@im=gcin\": #Set gcin as the XIM Input Server\n"
msgstr ""
"#Users who do not wish to use monetary units or time formats\n"
"#of Taiwan can manually change each variable\n"
"me:\\\n"
"\t:lang=zh_TW.Big5:\\\n"
"\t:setenv=LC_ALL=zh_TW.Big5,LC_COLLATE=zh_TW.Big5,LC_CTYPE=zh_TW.Big5,LC_MESSAGES=zh_TW.Big5,LC_MONETARY=zh_TW.Big5,LC_NUMERIC=zh_TW.Big5,LC_TIME=zh_TW.Big5:\\\n"
"\t:charset=big5:\\\n"
"\t:xmodifiers=\"@im=gcin\": #Set gcin as the XIM Input Server\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:183
msgid ""
"Alternately, the superuser can configure all users of the system for localization.  The following variables in [.filename]#/etc/"
"login.conf# are used to set the locale and MIME character set:"
msgstr ""
"另外，超级用户可以对系统的所有用户进行本地化配置。在 [.filename]#/etc/login.conf# 中的以下变量用于设置 locale 和 MIME 字符集："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:190
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"language_name|Account Type Description:\\\n"
"\t:charset=MIME_charset:\\\n"
"\t:lang=locale_name:\\\n"
"\t:tc=default:\n"
msgstr ""
"language_name|Account Type Description:\\\n"
"\t:charset=MIME_charset:\\\n"
"\t:lang=locale_name:\\\n"
"\t:tc=default:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:193
msgid "So, the previous Latin-1 example would look like this:"
msgstr "因此，之前的 Latin-1 例子会是这样的："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:200
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"german|German Users Accounts:\\\n"
"\t:charset=ISO-8859-1:\\\n"
"\t:lang=de_DE.ISO8859-1:\\\n"
"\t:tc=default:\n"
msgstr ""
"german|German Users Accounts:\\\n"
"\t:charset=ISO-8859-1:\\\n"
"\t:lang=de_DE.ISO8859-1:\\\n"
"\t:tc=default:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:204
msgid "See man:login.conf[5] for more details about these variables.  Note that it already contains pre-defined _russian_ class."
msgstr "关于这些变量的更多细节，见 man:login.conf[5]。注意，它已经包含了预先定义的俄语类。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:206
msgid ""
"Whenever [.filename]#/etc/login.conf# is edited, remember to execute the following command to update the capability database:"
msgstr "每当编辑 [.filename]#/etc/login.conf# 时，记得执行以下命令来更新能力数据库。"

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:210
#, no-wrap
msgid "# cap_mkdb /etc/login.conf\n"
msgstr "# cap_mkdb /etc/login.conf\n"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:215
msgid ""
"For an end user, the `cap_mkdb` command will need to be run on their [.filename]#~/.login_conf# for any changes to take effect."
msgstr "对于终端用户来说，`cap_mkdb` 命令需要在他们的 [.filename]#~/.login_conf# 上运行，以使任何改变生效。"

#. type: Title =====
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:217
#, no-wrap
msgid "Utilities Which Change Login Classes"
msgstr "改变登录类别的实用程序"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:220
msgid ""
"In addition to manually editing [.filename]#/etc/login.conf#, several utilities are available for setting the locale for newly "
"created users."
msgstr "除了手动编辑 [.filename]#/etc/login.conf# 之外，还有几个工具可以用来为新创建的用户设置 locale。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:222
msgid "When using `vipw` to add new users, specify the _language_ to set the locale:"
msgstr "当使用 `vipw` 添加新用户时，指定语言来设置 locale："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:226
#, no-wrap
msgid "user:password:1111:11:language:0:0:User Name:/home/user:/bin/sh\n"
msgstr "user:password:1111:11:language:0:0:User Name:/home/user:/bin/sh\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:229
msgid ""
"When using `adduser` to add new users, the default language can be pre-configured for all new users or specified for an "
"individual user."
msgstr "当使用 `adduser` 添加新用户时，默认语言可以为所有新用户预先配置，也可以为单个用户指定。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:231
msgid "If all new users use the same language, set `defaultclass=_language_` in [.filename]#/etc/adduser.conf#."
msgstr "如果所有新用户都使用相同的语言，在 [.filename]#/etc/adduser.conf# 中设置`defaultclass=_language_`。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:233
msgid "To override this setting when creating a user, either input the required locale at this prompt:"
msgstr "要在创建用户时覆盖这个设置，可以在这个提示下输入所需的地区语言："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:237
#, no-wrap
msgid "Enter login class: default []:\n"
msgstr "Enter login class: default []:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:240
msgid "or specify the locale to set when invoking `adduser`:"
msgstr "或者在调用 `adduser` 时指定要设置的 locale："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:244
#, no-wrap
msgid "# adduser -class language\n"
msgstr "# adduser -class language\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:247
msgid "If `pw` is used to add new users, specify the locale as follows:"
msgstr "如果使用 `pw` 来添加新的用户，请按以下方式指定 locale："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:251
#, no-wrap
msgid "# pw useradd user_name -L language\n"
msgstr "# pw useradd user_name -L language\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:255
msgid ""
"To change the login class of an existing user, `chpass` can be used.  Invoke it as superuser and provide the username to edit "
"as the argument."
msgstr "要改变一个现有用户的登录类别，可以使用 `chpass`。以超级用户身份调用它，并提供要编辑的用户名作为参数："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:259
#, no-wrap
msgid "# chpass user_name\n"
msgstr "# chpass user_name\n"

#. type: Title ====
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:263
#, no-wrap
msgid "Shell Startup File Method"
msgstr "shell 启动文件方法"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:268
msgid ""
"This second method is not recommended as each shell that is used requires manual configuration, where each shell has a "
"different configuration file and differing syntax.  As an example, to set the German language for the `sh` shell, these lines "
"could be added to [.filename]#~/.profile# to set the shell for that user only.  These lines could also be added to [.filename]#/"
"etc/profile# or [.filename]#/usr/share/skel/dot.profile# to set that shell for all users:"
msgstr ""
"这第二种方法不被推荐，因为每个使用的 shell 都需要手动配置，每个 shell 都有不同的配置文件和不同的语法。举个例子，为了给 `sh` "
"shell 设置德语，可以在 [.filename]#~/.profile# 中加入这些行，以设置仅适用于该用户的 shell。这些行也可以添加到 "
"[.filename]#/etc/profile# 或 [.filename]#/usr/share/skel/dot.profile# 中，以便为所有用户设置该 shell："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/l10n/_index.adoc:273
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"LANG=de_DE.ISO8859-1; export LANG\n"
"MM_CHARSET=ISO-8859-1; export MM_CHARSET\n"
msgstr ""
